## Supported Markets
- Bitcoin (BTC)
- Ethereum (ETH)
- Tether (USDT)
- BNB (BNB)
- Cardano (ADA)
- Solana (SOL)
- XRP (XRP)
- Polkadot (DOT)

## Market Data Sources
Primary: CoinMarketCap API
Secondary: Binance API
Fallback: CoinGecko API

## Trading Pairs
BTC/USD
ETH/USD
BNB/USD
USDT/USD

## Price Update Interval
Real-time: WebSocket connection
Fallback: 5 seconds polling

## Market Hours
24/7 Trading Available

## Fee Structure
Trading Fee: 0.1%
Withdrawal Fee: Variable by cryptocurrency
Deposit Fee: Free